#: ../../source/api/prepshot._model.investment.rst:2
msgid "investment"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:1
msgid ""
"This module is used to determine investment-related constraints. The "
"model computes the retirement of each technology and transmission line "
"with these considerations:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:5
msgid ""
"The historical capacity of the technology and transmission line is based "
"on its capacity ratio."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:7
msgid "Each planning and scheduling period is based on the existing capacity."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:9
msgid ""
"The existing capacity for each year, in each zone, for each technology, "
"is as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:12
msgid ""
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}=\n"
"\\sum_{{\\rm{age}}=1}^{{{T}}_e\n"
"-(y-y_{\\rm{start}})}{{\\rm{CAP}}}_{{\\rm{age}},z,e}^{\\rm{inittech}}\n"
"+\\sum_{y_{\\rm{pre}}={\\max}(y_{\\rm{start}}, y-{{T}}_e)}^{y}\n"
"{{\\rm{cap}}_{y_{\\rm{pre}},z,e}^{\\rm{invtech}}}\\quad\\forall y,z,e"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:20
msgid ""
"The existing capacity of the transmission lines for each year, from "
":math:`z_{\\rm{from}}` zone to :math:`z_{\\rm{to}}`-th zone, is as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.investment:24
msgid ""
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z_{\\rm{from}},z_{\\rm{to}}}^{\\rm{existingline}}=\n"
"\\sum_{{\\rm{age}}=1}^{{T}_{\\rm{line}}\n"
"-(y-y_{\\rm{start}})}{{\\rm{CAP}}}_{{\\rm{age}},z_{\\rm{from}},\n"
"z_{\\rm{to}}}^{\\rm{initline}}\n"
"+\\sum_{y_{\\rm{pre}}={\\max}(y_{\\rm{start}}, y-{{T}}_{\\rm{line}})}^{y}"
"\n"
"{{\\rm{cap}}_{y_{\\rm{pre}},\n"
"z_{\\rm{from}},z_{\\rm{to}}}^{\\rm{invline}}}\\quad\\forall\n"
"y,z_{\\rm{from}}\\neq z_{\\rm{to}}"
msgstr ""

